The TYPE_MISMATCH is only caught when the query actually runs against a real ClickHouse server. This is an inherent limitation of the mocking strategy — it validates application logic around ClickHouse but not SQL correctness.\n\n**Environment note:** The `.env.local` file is missing from this repo (not committed, as intended). The local ClickHouse instance runs without a password, but `src/lib/clickhouse.ts` defaults `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD` to `\"password\"`. HTTP checks require either a `.env.local` with `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD=` (empty string) or setting the environment variable before starting the dev server. This is an environment setup gap, not an implementation bug — but it should be documented for new contributors.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01DrxGN4JEL8xyHB5gUGVHDV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Score: 5/10 — NEEDS_WORK**\n\nAll Phase A checks pass cleanly (tests, lint, type check, build). Phase B (HTTP check) reveals a critical runtime bug:\n\n**The bug:** `src/app/api/schema/route.ts:43` uses `ARRAY JOIN arrayJoin(JSONExtractKeys(properties)) AS property_key`. This is invalid ClickHouse SQL — `arrayJoin()` is a table function that already expands into scalar `String` rows; wrapping it in an `ARRAY JOIN` clause (which requires `Array` or `Map` type) causes a TYPE_MISMATCH error (code 53), returning HTTP 500 on every request.\n\n**Fix:** Change that line to `ARRAY JOIN JSONExtractKeys(properties) AS property_key` — verified to work against ClickHouse v26.4.1.951.\n\n**Why unit tests missed it:** The ClickHouse client is fully mocked, so the SQL string is never parsed by a real server. Only the HTTP integration check caught this.\n\nSecondary note: with the corrected query, events with `{}` empty properties won't appear in `event_names` (ARRAY JOIN drops empty-array rows). This is a spec conformance gap but non-blocking."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1356,"cache_read_input_tokens":56085,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1356},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bf5c5d54-f5be-4f7e-81c9-7cee309979d4","uuid":"3061ed49-eef0-46b2-8016-be079457fbf8"}
